{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"It has been 128 years"},{"time":4840,"text":"since the last country\nin the world abolished slavery"},{"time":9240,"text":"and 53 years"},{"time":11680,"text":"since Martin Luther King pronounced\nhis \"I Have A Dream\" speech."},{"time":17800,"text":"But we still live in a world"},{"time":20000,"text":"where the color of our skin\nnot only gives a first impression,"},{"time":25880,"text":"but a lasting one that remains."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31120,"text":"I was born in a family full of colors."},{"time":35400,"text":"My father is the son of a maid"},{"time":38440,"text":"from whom he inherited\nan intense dark chocolate tone."},{"time":44280,"text":"He was adopted by those\nwho I know as my grandparents."},{"time":49000,"text":"The matriarch, my grandma,"},{"time":51280,"text":"has a porcelain skin and cotton-like hair."},{"time":55560,"text":"My grandpa was somewhere between\na vanilla and strawberry yogurt tone,"},{"time":61320,"text":"like my uncle and my cousin."},{"time":64680,"text":"My mother is a cinnamon-skin\ndaughter of a native Brazilian,"},{"time":71560,"text":"with a pinch of hazel and honey,"},{"time":74920,"text":"and a man [who is]\na mix of coffee with milk,"},{"time":77880,"text":"but with a lot of coffee."},{"time":80400,"text":"She has two sisters."},{"time":82680,"text":"One in a toasted-peanut skin"},{"time":85600,"text":"and the other,"},{"time":87040,"text":"also adopted,"},{"time":88600,"text":"more on the beige side,"},{"time":90520,"text":"like a pancake."}]},{"cues":[{"time":91840,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93240,"text":"Growing up in this family,"},{"time":96120,"text":"color was never important for me."},{"time":99600,"text":"Outside home, however,\nthings were different soon."},{"time":105560,"text":"Color had many other meanings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110160,"text":"I remember my first\ndrawing lessons in school"},{"time":113960,"text":"as a bunch of contradictory feelings."},{"time":116920,"text":"It was exciting and creative"},{"time":119880,"text":"but I never understood\nthe unique flesh-colored pencil."},{"time":125360,"text":"I was made of flesh but I wasn't pink."},{"time":128759,"text":"My skin was brown,\nand people said I was black."},{"time":132560,"text":"I was seven years old\nwith a mess of colors in my head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137960,"text":"Later,"},{"time":139880,"text":"when I took my cousin to school,"},{"time":142400,"text":"I was usually taken for the nanny."},{"time":145320,"text":"By helping in the kitchen\nat a friend's party,"},{"time":149000,"text":"people thought I was the maid."},{"time":151680,"text":"I was even treated like a prostitute"},{"time":154720,"text":"just because I was walking alone\non the beach with European friends."},{"time":159760,"text":"And many times,"},{"time":161280,"text":"visiting my grandma or friends\nin upper class buildings,"},{"time":165880,"text":"I was invited not to use\nthe main elevator."},{"time":170840,"text":"Because in the end,"},{"time":173240,"text":"with this color and this hair,"},{"time":175960,"text":"I cannot belong to some places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":180400,"text":"In some way,"},{"time":181640,"text":"I get to used to it and accept part of it."},{"time":185200,"text":"However, something inside of me\nkeeps revolving and struggling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191200,"text":"Years later I married a Spaniard."},{"time":195440,"text":"But not any Spaniard."},{"time":197640,"text":"I chose one with the skin color\nof a lobster when sunburnt."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":203600,"text":"Since then, a new question\nstarted to chase me."},{"time":207960,"text":"What will be the color of your children?"},{"time":211040,"text":"As you can understand,\nthis is my last concern."},{"time":214280,"text":"But thinking about it,"},{"time":217000,"text":"with my previous background,"},{"time":218960,"text":"my story led me to make\nmy personal exercise as a photographer."},{"time":225080,"text":"And that is how Humanae was born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228640,"text":"Humanae is a pursuit\nto highlight our true colors,"},{"time":233600,"text":"rather than the untrue"},{"time":235280,"text":"white, red, black or yellow\nassociated with race."},{"time":240720,"text":"It's a kind of game to question our codes."},{"time":245080,"text":"It's a work in progress\nfrom a personal story to a global history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250160,"text":"I portray the subjects\nin a white background."},{"time":255880,"text":"Then I choose an 11-pixel\nsquare from the nose,"},{"time":260800,"text":"paint the background,"},{"time":263200,"text":"and look for the corresponding color\nin the industrial palette, Pantone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268480,"text":"I started with my family and friends,"},{"time":271480,"text":"then more and more people\njoined the adventure,"},{"time":275400,"text":"thanks to public calls\ncoming through the social media."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280440,"text":"I thought that the main space\nto show my work was the Internet"},{"time":285040,"text":"because I want an open concept\nthat invites everybody"},{"time":289600,"text":"to push the share button\nin both the computer and their brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":296280,"text":"The snowball started to roll."},{"time":299880,"text":"The project had a great welcome --"},{"time":303760,"text":"invitations, exhibitions,"},{"time":307240,"text":"physical formats,"},{"time":309000,"text":"galleries and museums ..."},{"time":311800,"text":"just happened."},{"time":313560,"text":"And among them, my favorite:"},{"time":317240,"text":"when Humanae occupies public spaces"},{"time":321280,"text":"and appears in the street,"},{"time":324440,"text":"it fosters a popular debate"},{"time":327840,"text":"and creates a feeling of community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334800,"text":"I have portrayed more than 3,000 people"},{"time":338920,"text":"in 13 different countries,"},{"time":341560,"text":"19 different cities around the world."},{"time":344640,"text":"Just to mention some of them --"},{"time":347200,"text":"from someone included in the Forbes list,"},{"time":349760,"text":"to refugees who crossed\nthe Mediterranean by boat."},{"time":353240,"text":"In Paris, from the UNESCO\nHeadquarters to a shelter."},{"time":357680,"text":"And students both in Switzerland\nand favelas in Rio de Janeiro."}]},{"cues":[{"time":363360,"text":"All kinds of beliefs,"},{"time":365360,"text":"gender identities"},{"time":366920,"text":"or physical impairments,"},{"time":369160,"text":"a newborn or terminally ill."},{"time":372160,"text":"We all together build Humanae."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377040,"text":"Those portraits make us rethink\nhow we see each other."},{"time":382120,"text":"When modern science\nis questioning the race concept,"},{"time":386000,"text":"what does it mean for us\nto be black, white, yellow, red?"},{"time":392560,"text":"Is it the eye, the nose,\nthe mouth, the hair?"},{"time":397720,"text":"Or does it have to do with our origin,"},{"time":401080,"text":"nationality"},{"time":402360,"text":"or bank account?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406880,"text":"This personal exercise\nturned out to be a discovery."},{"time":411640,"text":"Suddenly I realized that Humanae\nwas useful for many people."},{"time":417880,"text":"It represents a sort of mirror"},{"time":420160,"text":"for those who cannot find\nthemselves reflected in any label."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425320,"text":"It was amazing"},{"time":426640,"text":"that people started to share\ntheir thoughts about the work with me."},{"time":431080,"text":"I have hundreds of that,"},{"time":433080,"text":"I will share with you, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435880,"text":"A mother of 11 years --"},{"time":438760,"text":"A mother of an 11-year-old girl wrote me,"},{"time":443080,"text":"\"Very good for me as a tool\nto work on her confidence,"},{"time":446880,"text":"as this past weekend"},{"time":448960,"text":"one of her girlfriends argued with her\nthat she does not belong"},{"time":453920,"text":"and should not be allowed\nto live in Norway."},{"time":458000,"text":"So your work has\na very special place in my heart"},{"time":461960,"text":"and it's very important for me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":466880,"text":"A woman shared her portrait\non Facebook and wrote,"},{"time":471640,"text":"\"All my life,"},{"time":472880,"text":"people from across the globe\nhad difficulties to place me in a group,"},{"time":478000,"text":"a stereotype,"},{"time":479480,"text":"a box."},{"time":480800,"text":"Perhaps we should stop."},{"time":483000,"text":"Instead of framing, ask the individual,"},{"time":486160,"text":"'How would you label yourself?'"},{"time":488480,"text":"Then I would say,"},{"time":490320,"text":"'Hi. I'm Massiel."},{"time":492360,"text":"I'm a Dominican-Dutch,"},{"time":493920,"text":"I grew up in a mixed family"},{"time":495960,"text":"and I'm a bisexual woman.' \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":499880,"text":"Besides these unexpected\nand touching reactions,"},{"time":504000,"text":"Humanae finds a new life\nin a different variety of fields."},{"time":508680,"text":"Just to show you some examples,"},{"time":511680,"text":"illustrators and art students"},{"time":513919,"text":"using it as a reference\nfor their sketches and their studies."},{"time":518039,"text":"It's a collection of faces."}]},{"cues":[{"time":520840,"text":"Researchers in the fields of anthropology,"},{"time":524800,"text":"physics and neuroscience"},{"time":527120,"text":"use Humanae with different\nscientific approaches"},{"time":531280,"text":"related to human ethnicity,"},{"time":533920,"text":"optophysiology,"},{"time":535680,"text":"face recognition"},{"time":537440,"text":"or Alzheimer's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540000,"text":"One of the most important\nimpacts of the project"},{"time":543440,"text":"is that Humanae was chosen\nto be the cover of Foreign Affairs,"},{"time":548120,"text":"one of the most relevant\npolitical publications."},{"time":552760,"text":"And talking about foreign affairs,"},{"time":556280,"text":"I found the perfect\nambassadors for my project ..."},{"time":560680,"text":"teachers."},{"time":561920,"text":"They are the ones that use Humanae\nas a tool for educational purposes."},{"time":568880,"text":"Their passion encourages me\nto go back to drawing classes,"},{"time":574360,"text":"but this time as a teacher myself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578200,"text":"My students,"},{"time":579680,"text":"both adults and kids,"},{"time":581960,"text":"paint their self-portraits,"},{"time":584760,"text":"trying to discover\ntheir own unique color."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596720,"text":"As a photographer,"},{"time":598760,"text":"I realize that I can be a channel\nfor others to communicate."},{"time":605040,"text":"As an individual,"},{"time":606880,"text":"as Angélica,"},{"time":609080,"text":"every time I take a picture,"},{"time":612280,"text":"I feel that I am sitting\nin front of a therapist."},{"time":617480,"text":"All the frustration, fear and loneliness"},{"time":622440,"text":"that I once felt ..."},{"time":624360,"text":"becomes love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":629400,"text":"The last country --"},{"time":632000,"text":"the last country in the world\nwho abolished slavery"},{"time":637040,"text":"is the country where I was born,"},{"time":639920,"text":"Brazil."},{"time":642440,"text":"We still have to work hard\nto abolish discrimination."},{"time":648080,"text":"That remains a common practice worldwide,"},{"time":652080,"text":"and that will not disappear by itself."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":657760,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671880,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}